\" />"},{"pid":"61172c96cda202095522bce72ebed066ef178800","tid":2078603,"uid":220601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"71 71 71 71 71"},{"pid":"ec21df201ab1c5007fd663934f99c17126b10787","tid":2078603,"uid":20558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c287422e6277b18e54b4cc03424d2356047ebdc7","tid":2078603,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"希望樓主pin，G20聯署今晚deadline<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[全民反國安 - G20國聯署請願行動]<br />\n<br />\n國安法草案即將落實，預計有可能於下月實施。屆時，香港將失去獨立司法制度，對香港的人權及自由，本土營商、勞工環境以及各國的利益均會做成重大損害，而本港作為國際城巿的地位亦岌岌可危。<br />\n<br />\n為顯示香港人民反國安法，維護人權及公義的決心，主辦單位將聯同區議員及其他本土組織收集聯署，並向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處進行馬拉松式請願，尋求國際社會的支持，阻止中共破壞一國兩制，人權及香港司法獨立地位，維持獨立營商環境，及保障各國在港僑民福祉及商人的在港利益。<br />\n<br />\n以下為向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處聯署信內容:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c%2Fedit&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b7429029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n網上聯署 (2020年6月25日2359前):<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA%2Fviewform&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=5c8022d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n實體聯署表格 (請列印並邀請身邊的人簽署, 並於6月25(四)交往以下街站 (沙田小巴站, 1400-1700; 旺角 旺東橋 moko 入口, 1100-1700; 或朗豪坊雅蘭對出, 1400-1900):<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=0bec8e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/10bIZEDuFWiVibPR8vRCk4AtuyCwisPf3/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法實施後，港人將面對中共的白色恐怖，言論、結社、新聞自由等基本人權將不復存在。主辦單位懇請各位港人把握機會，合力爭取。<br />\n<br />\n全民反國安，還我真香港！香港人，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n主辦 :<br />\n香港會計手足工會<br />\n香港金融業職工總會<br />\n政府非公務員職工總會<br />\n香港貿易推銷及採購職工會<br />\n香港旅遊業革新總工會<br />\n香港資訊科技界工會<br />\n香港寵物界工會<br />\n社會及政治組織從業員工會<br />\n香港調酒師工會<br />\n香港幼兒教育工作者工會<br />\n香港設計師工會<br />\n<br />\n［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077187</a><br />\n<br />\nFB Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGeneralStrike9293/posts/290804232294947?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGeneralStrike9293%2Fposts%2F290804232294947%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=01367e90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGeneralStrike9293/posts/290804232294947?__tn__=-R</a>"},{"pid":"9291b8563f175be65f629149c2bb0bad1c51c55c","tid":2078603,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5a1a4876fbb59a3840e88279482c81c1a8ad55f","tid":2078603,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ef